comments: Oubre Jr. (GSW) reaches in and makes contact to Siakam's (TOR) arm that affects his SQBR.
Siakam (TOR) and Green (GSW) briefly engage and disengage on the perimeter.
Boucher (TOR) makes contact to Curry's (GSW) arm that affects his ability to follow through during his driving shot attempt.
Bazemore (GSW) and Lowry (TOR) make marginal contact with each other as they establish position on the perimeter.
Green (GSW) is in a legal guarding position and cleanly blocks VanVleet's (TOR) driving shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) makes marginal contact with Bazemore's (GSW) non-shooting arm that does not affect his shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) dribbles, places both hands on the ball, and then continues his dribble.
Green (GSW) is retreating his arms into a vertical position when he makes marginal contact with VanVleet's (TOR) non-shooting arm.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Curry (GSW) loses the ball out of bounds.  After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Warriors possession is confirmed.
Powell (TOR) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Wiggins' (GSW) path and he absorbs the contact.
Curry (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position during Siakam's (TOR) drive to the basket and he makes clean contact with the ball.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Warriors possession is confirmed.
Siakam (TOR) briefly places an arm at Green's (GSW) side but does not affect his FOM.
Lowry (TOR) reaches in and makes contact to Lee's (GSW) arm before the start of his upward shooting motion.  After communicating with the Replay Center, a common foul is ruled.
Wiggins (GSW) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Siakam (TOR) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
